== 發行 ==
這部影片是DVD發行的錄影帶首映版，美國於2008年8月26日發行，英國和歐洲於2008年9月22日發行。該DVD包含刪除片段，由導演主持的生產花絮、遊戲和活動，並通過[[塞爾芮·博格斯|塞爾芮·博格斯]]對[[小美人魚音樂劇|小美人魚音樂劇]]的生產花絮特輯。12月16日，該片白金版與《[[小美人魚|小美人魚]]》和《[[小美人魚2：重返大海|小美人魚2：重返大海]]》的“小美人魚三部曲”合集一同發行。

== 評價 ==
該DVD在那年8月31日結束的一周成為了最暢銷的DVD。<ref>{{cite news | author=Arnold Thomas | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3i0532517b5fc5d6afa87cc17b45a2acc7 | title=Ariel has new 'Beginning' on DVD | publisher=HollywoodReporter | date=2008-09-03 | accessdate=2008-09-08 }} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref> 這部電影的評論普遍是正面的，雖然新的反派Marina一直被批評為像是一個貧窮的烏蘇拉。<ref name=sister /><ref name="blogcritic">{{cite news | author=Sombrero Grande | url=http://blogcritics.org/archives/2008/08/26/003134.php | title=DVD Review: The Little Mermaid - Ariel's Beginning | publisher=Blog Critic | date=2008-08-26 | accessdate=2008-09-08 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080829164503/http://blogcritics.org/archives/2008/08/26/003134.php | archivedate=2008-08-29 }}</ref><ref name="dvdverdict">{{cite news | author=Michael Stailey | url=http://www.dvdverdict.com/reviews/arielsbeginning.php | title=The Little Mermaid: Ariel's Beginning at DVD Verdict | publisher=DVD Verdict | date= | accessdate=2008-09-08 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080905234018/http://www.dvdverdict.com/reviews/arielsbeginning.php | archivedate=2008-09-05 }}</ref>影片的動畫品質一直稱讚為一個令人印象深刻和媲美原電影的錄影帶首映影片。<ref name="blogcritic" /><ref name="toonzone">{{cite news | author=90'sCartoonMan | url=http://news.toonzone.net/article.php?ID=25754/ | title="The Little Mermaid: Ariel's Beginning": How To Keep Fish Fresh | publisher=Toon Zone | date=2008-09-01 | accessdate=2008-09-10 }}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> 負面評價是在電影內，愚笨時常被建立在無聊的故事下，這實在太普通，影響到人物在困境時所流露的情感魅力。<ref>{{cite news | author=David Cornelius | url=http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/34451/little-mermaid-ariels-beginning-the/ | title=DVD Talk Review: The Little Mermaid: Ariel's Beginning | publisher=DVD Talk | date=2008-08-27 | accessdate=2008-09-08 | archive-date=2009-07-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090730193218/http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/34451/little-mermaid-ariels-beginning-the/ | dead-url=no }}</ref> 音樂也被批評為不容易記住的，評論它是個不實的宣傳。<ref name="dvdverdict" /><ref name="toonzone" />

